OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Fheavy rain spreading eastwards. Rain
OL,7,Fclears to the east overnight with dry
OL,8,Fconditions by morning. Strong to gale
OL,9,Fforce southeasterly winds easing
OL,10,Finland later in the night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA largely dry day with
OL,13,Fbright spells. Scattered showers from
OL,14,Flate afternoon through the evening.
OL,15,FStrong winds around the coast with
OL,16,Fwinds strengthening inland later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
